data.description:
Check out this wonderfully updated and maintained home in the heart of Dexter, Maine! This property offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.
Boasting three bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this home is ideal for those seeking extra space. 
The property features barn space providing storage solutions or possibly vehicle parking. You'll also appreciate the paved driveway, and front porch. 
This home is situated on a generous 1.10-acre lot. The large back yard is full of perennials and tons of space to garden or play. Roses, peonies, grapes, and more!
Located in a desirable setting just off Main Street, this home combines the allure of rural living with proximity to local amenities and services. 
Don't miss the chance to make this house your home! Contact us today to schedule a viewing.
